ster%20Meloni's%20two%20visits%20to%20India%20last%20year%20were%20instrumental%20in%20infusing%20momentum%20and%20depth%20in%20our%20bilateral%20agenda.%20We%20remain%20committed%20to%20consolidate%20the%20India-Italy%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20and%20bolster%20cooperation%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20and%20the%20Mediterranean%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20discussions%20at%20the%20Outreach%20session%2C%20the%20focus%20would%20be%20on%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20energy%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20the%20Mediterranean.%20It%20will%20be%20an%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20greater%20synergy%20between%20the%20outcomes%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20held%20under%20India's%20Presidency%20and%20the%20forthcoming%20G7%20Summit%20and%20deliberate%20on%20issues%20which%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%20I%20am%20also%20looking%20forward%20to%20meeting%20other%20leaders%20participating%20in%20the%20summit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20hosted%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20last%20September%2C%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20the%20world%20leaders%20gathering%20at%20the%20Apulia%20meet%20being%20held%20under%20the%20Italian%20presidency.%20The%20Italian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Georgia%20Meloni%2C%20will%20welcome%20PM%20Modi%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20of%20Italy%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20opening%20address%20on%20Thursday%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20G7%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20Japanese%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%2C%20European%20Commission%20President%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20and%20European%20Council%20President%20Charles%20Michel%20%E2%80%93%20she%20said%20southern%20Italy%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20venue%20to%20send%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20no%20coincidence%20that%20we%20are%20hosting%20the%20summit%20in%20Apulia.%20We%20did%20this%20because%20Apulia%20is%20a%20region%20of%20southern%20Italy%20and%20the%20message%20we%20want%20to%20launch%20is%20that%20the%20G7%2C%20under%20the%20Italian%20presidency%2C%20wishes%20to%20strengthen%20its%20dialogue%20with%20the%20nations%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%26quot%3B%20Meloni%20said%20in%20her%20opening%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20is%20set%20to%20dominate%20the%20agenda%20as%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20arrived%20for%20the%20discussions%20on%20Thursday.%20While%20India%20has%20reiterated%20its%20stance%20on%20%26quot%3Bdialogue%20and%20diplomacy%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20best%20approach%2C%20Sunak%20is%20leading%20calls%20for%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%26quot%3B%20efforts%20to%20support%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20it%20takes%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20be%20decisive%20and%20creative%20in%20our%20efforts%20to%20support%20Ukraine%20and%20end%20%5BRussian%20President%5D%20Putin's%20illegal%20war%20at%20this%20critical%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sunak%2C%20who%20announced%20up%20to%20GBP%20242%20million%20in%20bilateral%20assistance%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20support%20of%20the%20country's%20immediate%20humanitarian%2C%20energy%20and%20stabilisation%20needs%2C%20and%20to%20lay%20the%20foundations%20for%20longer-term%20economic%20and%20social%20recovery%20and%20reconstruction.%20In%20his%20pre-visit%20media%20briefing%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20had%20recalled%20PM%20Modi's%20statement%20in%20September%202022%20that%20%26quot%3Btoday's%20era%20is%20not%20of%20war%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20always%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20to%20offer%20assistance%20wherever%20we%20can%20to%20alleviate%20challenges%20faced%20b