r.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20might%20be%20the%20third%20or%20fourth%20buyer%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20hadn't%20previously%20paid%20the%20taxes%2C%20the%20government%20could%20come%20after%20you%20for%20those%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9946f85-a550-4598-a0fe-41df76897ef1%5C%22%3E2.%20Make%20sure%20the%20street%20leading%20to%20your%20plot%20has%20a%20name%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20looking%20for%20leasehold%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-couple-investment-property-villa-bali-retirement-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproperty%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20make%20sure%20there's%20a%20public%20road%20leading%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20times%20when%20property%20has%20been%20locked%20in%2C%20because%20it%20might%20look%20like%20there's%20a%20road%20there%20to%20the%20land%20you're%20looking%20at.%20However%2C%20that%20road%20could%20be%20on%20land%20that%20belongs%20to%20someone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20street%20doesn't%20have%20a%20name%2C%20you%20might%20be%20in%20for%20trouble.%20There%20have%20been%20cases%20of%20properties%20being%20built%20on%20land%20without%20registered%20roads%20or%20laneway%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20could%20be%20a%20road%20there%20when%20you%20went%20and%20looked%20at%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20you%20look%20it%20up%20on%20Google%2C%20it%20won't%20have%20a%20name%2C%20which%20means%20that%20someone%20owns%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f4688784-97f9-49e7-8267-826f0a97e6d3%5C%22%3E3.%20You%20might%20not%20want%20to%20live%20in%20the%20same%20place%20you%20vacation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20get%20a%20yearly%20rental%2C%20test%20an%20area%20first%20before%20you%20commit%20to%20buying%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20said.%20%26quot%3BJust%20because%20you've%20holidayed%20in%20Seminyak%20mig