%20can%20last%20a%20lot%20longer%2C%20Jeremy%20Siegel%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jeremy%20siegel%20point%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F636d366e951bdc00182d899e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWharton%20Professor%20Jeremy%20Siegel%20says%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20undergoing%20a%20credit%20crunch.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20momentum%20trade%20driving%20market%20gains%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%2C%20says%20WisdomTree's%20Jeremy%20Siegel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BOften%20times%20it%20gets%20overdone%20at%20the%20end%2C%20but%20the%20end%20is%20often%20further%20into%20the%20future%20than%20many%20people%20believe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESiegel%20forecasts%20stocks%20will%20outperform%20bonds%20over%20three%20to%20five%20years%2C%20delivering%20real%20returns%20of%20about%205%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20momentum%20trade%20that%20has%20powered%20the%20stock%20market%20higher%20over%20the%20past%20year-and-a-half%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20on%20for%20a%20lot%20longer%20than%20most%20expect%2C%20according%20to%20WisdomTree%20economist%20Jeremy%20Siegel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiegel%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%20that%20gains%20seen%20in%20AI%20stocks%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fbroadcom-stock-earnings-record-price-trillion-market-cap-ai-revenue-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%2C%20Broadcom%2C%20and%20others%20are%20showing%20no%20sign%20of%20slowing%20down.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20momentum%20trade%20on%20the%20tech%20and%20AI-related%20is%20still%20there.%20That%20has%20been%20so%20powerful.%20It%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20bad%20news%20to%20break%20a%20momentum%20trade%20and%20we%20just%20haven't%20gotten%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20up%20about%2014%25%20year-to-date%2C%20the%20tech-heavy%20Nasdaq%20100%20is%2017%25%20and%20Nvidia%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apolloacademy.com%2Fextreme-concentration-in-returns-in-the-sp-500%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20is%20responsible%20for%2035%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20year-to-date%20return%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20up%20a%20whopping%20162%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLet's%20face%20it%2C%20those%20stocks%20have%20delivered%20the%20bacon%20as%20they%20say%2C%20and%20as%20long%20as%20they%20do%2C%20those%20momentum%20traders%20are%20going%20to%20crowd%20into%20those%20stocks%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20see%20that%20ending%20anytime%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20often%20times%20it%20gets%20over%20done%20at%20the%20end%2C%20but%20the%20end%20is%20often%20further%20into%20the%20future%20than%20many%20people%20believe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Carson%20Group's%20Facts%20vs.%20Feelings%20podcast%2C%20Siegel%20highlighted%20a%20personal%20anecdote%20as%20to%20why%20it's%20so%20hard%20to%20call%20the%20top%20in%20a%20stock%20market%20bubble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20very%20good%20colleague%20at%20Wharton%E2%80%A6%20he%20started%20shorting%20internet%20stocks%20in%201999.%20They%20were%20way%20overvalued%20then.%20But%20he%20got%20margin%20calls%20and%20eventually%20had%20to%20cover%20his%20shorts%20at%20the%20top%2C%26quot%3B%20Siegel%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20really%20hard%20to%20bet%20on%20a%20bubble.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Siegel%20doesn't%20believe%20today's%20stock%20market%20is%20in%20a%20bubble%20because%2C%20unlike%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20earnings%20are%20actually%20backing%20up%20today's%20record-high%20stock%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20the%20current%20AI%20is%20a%20bubble.%20Look%20at%20Nvidia