20break%20the%20plumbing%20and%20flood%20my%20apartment%3F%20Did%20I%20need%20to%20leave%20the%20water%20on%20for%20the%20whole%20time%3F%20How%20would%20I%20dry%20my%20clothes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20some%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20I've%20learned%20just%20how%20convenient%20a%20portable%20washer%20can%20be.%20I've%20gained%20back%20hours%20of%20my%20time%20and%20managed%20to%20save%20a%20bit%20of%20money%20too.%20Here's%20what%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20buying%20and%20using%20a%20portable%20washer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Who%20should%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20should%20buy%20a%20portable%20washing%20machine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20laundry%20in%20your%20apartment%20building%20or%20home%2C%20a%20portable%20washer%20is%20a%20lifesaver%20and%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20an%20absolute%20must.%20It%20gives%20you%20full%20and%20exclusive%20access%20to%20laundry%20right%20in%20your%20kitchen%20or%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you%20do%20have%20communal%20laundry%2C%20a%20portable%20washer%20can%20offer%20a%20much%20more%20personal%20and%20reliable%20option%3A%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20machines%20to%20be%20free%2C%20acquire%20a%20giant%20bag%20of%20quarters%2C%20or%20worry%20about%20someone%20taking%20your%20wet%20laundry%20out%20and%20dropping%20it%20onto%20a%20dirty%20counter.%20They're%20also%20popular%20in%20RV%20and%20boating%20communities%20and%20can%20be%20a%20good%20option%20for%20tiny%20houses%2C%20apartments%2C%20and%20some%20dorm%20rooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Which%20machine%20should%20you%20buy%3F%5C%22%3EWhich%20portable%20washing%20machine%20should%20you%20buy%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20many%20different%20styles%20of%20portable%20washers%2C%20but%20a%20good%20product%20should%20be%20compact%2C%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20and%20energy-efficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20much%20research%2C%20I%20purchased%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5