tice%20For%20Encroachment%20In%20Gujarat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP-ruled%20Vadodara%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(VMC)%20in%20Gujarat%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20former%20India%20cricketer%20and%20recently%20elected%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Baharampur%20Yusuf%20Pathan%20for%20allegedly%20encroaching%20on%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20the%20civic%20body%20said%20belongs%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20notice%20was%20served%20to%20Mr%20Pathan%20on%20June%206%2C%20VMC's%20standing%20committee%20chairman%20Shital%20Mistry%20informed%20the%20media%20on%20Thursday%20after%20the%20issue%20was%20highlighted%20by%20former%20BJP%20corporator%20Vijay%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20reporters%20earlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20had%20alleged%20that%20though%20the%20state%20government%20had%20rejected%20VMC's%20proposal%20to%20sell%20the%20plot%20to%20Mr%20Pathan%20in%202012%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20MP%20had%20encroached%20on%20the%20plot%20by%20constructing%20a%20compound%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20any%20grudge%20against%20Yusuf%20Pathan.%20A%20plot%20in%20Tanadalja%20area%20under%20TP%2022%20is%20a%20residential%20plot%20owned%20by%20VMC.%20In%202012%2C%20Mr%20Pathan%20had%20demanded%20this%20plot%20from%20VMC%20because%20his%20house%2C%20which%20was%20under%20construction%20at%20that%20time%2C%20was%20adjacent%20to%20that%20plot.%20He%20had%20offered%20nearly%20Rs%2057%2C000%20per%20square%20meter%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20VMC%20at%20that%20time%20and%20it%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20general%20board%20meeting.%20However%2C%20the%20state%20government%2C%20which%20is%20the%20final%20authority%20in%20such%20matters%2C%20did%20not%20give%20its%20approval%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20the%20proposal%20was%20rejected%2C%20the%20VMC%20did%20not%20put%20up%20a%