eflated%20when%20she%20decided%20against%20contesting.%20The%20buzz%20has%20started%20gathering%20steam%20again%2C%20however%2C%20with%20sources%20telling%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20Congress%20leader%20may%20be%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20for%20the%20bypoll%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20if%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20vacates%20the%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20had%20won%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20-%20with%20considerable%20margins%20-%20from%20both%20the%20Raebareli%20and%20Wayanad%20constituencies%2C%20also%20fanned%20the%20flames%20of%20a%20possible%20debut%20by%20his%20sister%20when%20he%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20have%20lost%20%26quot%3Bby%20two-three%20lakh%20votes%26quot%3B%20if%20his%20sister%20had%20fought%20against%20him%20in%20Varanasi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong%20History%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'will%20she-won't%20she'%20around%20Ms%20Gandhi%20contesting%20elections%20has%20been%20around%20since%20at%20least%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20had%20been%20speculated%20that%20she%20could%20challenge%20PM%20Modi%20in%20the%20Varanasi%20constituency%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20struggling%20to%20halt%20the%20BJP%20juggernaut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20didn't%20happen%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20herself%20had%20said%20she%20wasn't%20ruling%20out%20contesting%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections%20in%202022%2C%20when%20she%20was%20the%20Congress%20General%20Secretary%20for%20the%20state.%20She%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20hinted%20that%20she%20could%20be%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20only%20to%20say%20hours%20later%20that%20she%20had%20meant%20it%20in%20a%20tongue-in-cheek%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20gave%20up%20the%20Raebareli%20seat%20-%20which%20she%20had%20held%20since%202004%20-%20and%20became%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20speculation%20was%20almost%20seen%20as%20a%20certainty.%20It%20was%20being%20reported%20that%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20would%20contest%20from%20Raebareli%20and%20her%20brother%20would%20fight%20to%20win%20back%20Amethi%20from%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20had%20said%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20asked%20the%20Gandhi%20siblings%20to%20take%20a%20decision%2C%20but%20had%20let%20it%20be%20known%20that%20he%20would%20like%20both%20to%20contest.%20He%20had%20also%20said%20that%20if%20they%20didn't%20fight%20from%20the%20bastions%2C%20it%20would%20send%20a%20wrong%20message%20to%20the%20workers%2C%20the%20Congress'%20allies%20in%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%2C%20had%2C%20however%20chosen%20not%20to%20contest.%20Sources%20close%20to%20her%20had%20said%20she%20had%20made%20the%20decision%20because%20if%20she%20also%20won%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20it%20would%20have%20led%20to%20three%20Gandhis%20being%20in%20Parliament%20-%20her%20mother%2C%20brother%20and%20her%20-%20lending%20credence%20to%20the%20BJP's%20dynastic%20politics%20charge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinning%20Call%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20had%20spent%20the%20bulk%20of%20her%20time%20campaigning%20in%20Raebareli%20and%20Amethi%2C%20both%20of%20which%20were%20won%20by%20her%20party%20with%20big%20margins.%20When%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20came%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party-Congress%20alliance%20shocked%20the%20BJP%20and%20pollsters%20by%20winning%2043%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%2080%20constituencies%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20alone%20moving%20up%20to%20six%20from%20its%202019%20tally%20of%20one.%20The%20BJP%2C%20which%20had%20clinched%2062%20constituencies%20last%20time%2C%20was%20reduced%20to%2033%2C%20four%20lower%20than%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party's%2037.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20results%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20also%20praised%20his%20sister's%20role%20while%20thanking%20the%20residents%20of%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERahul%20Gandhi's%20Dilemma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20contesting%20in%20the%20bypolls%20from%20Wayanad%20will%20hinge%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20deciding%20to%20give%20up%20the%20constituency%20-%20which%20had%20granted%20him%20a%20win%20when%20he%20had%20lost%20Amethi%20in%202019%20-%20in%20favour%20of%20Raebareli.%20While%20he%20had%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20is%20facing%20a%20dilemma%20and%20is%20still%20undecided%2C%20saying%20only%20that%20his%20final%20decision%20will%20make%20people%20from%20both%20constituencies%20happy%2C%20sources%20have%20said%20it%20is%20almost%20certain%20that%20he%20will%20choose%20to%20go%20with%20Raebareli%20because%20of%20UP's%20importance%20in%20national%20politics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20senior%20Congress%20functionaries%20have%20also%20made%20statements%20to%20this%20effect.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20key%20Gandhi%20family%20aide%2C%20who%20handed%20a%20shock%20defeat%20to%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20Amethi%2C%20has%20urged%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20retain%20the%20Raebareli%20seat%20while%20Kerala%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%20chief%20K%20Sudhakaran%20has%20hinted%20that%20the%20leader%20could%20relinquish%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20be%20saddened%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20who%20is%20supposed%20to%20lead%20the%20nation%20cannot%20be%20expected%20to%20remain%20in%20Wayanad.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20should%20not%20be%20sad.%20Everyone%20should%20understand%20that%20and%20give%20all%20their%20wishes%20and%20support%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sudhakaran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F