%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20TheLiverDoc%20(%40theliverdr)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftheliverdr%2Fstatus%2F1801095757690491028%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20elderly%20maid%20comes%20in%20and%20tells%20me%20she%20has%20seen%20this%20rash%20in%20her%20grandchildren%20and%20it's%20called%20'Anjaampani'%20in%20the%20local%20language%20(5th%20Disease)%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20and%20got%20checked%20for%20Parvovirus%20B19%20and%20it%20came%20positive%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Philips%20wrote.%26quot%3B17%20years%20of%20medical%20school%20and%20a%20Harrisons%20on%20my%20lap%20and%20my%20elderly%20maid%20got%20it%20in%20like%2010%20seconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedline%20Plus%20describes%20the%20fifth%20disease%2C%20also%20known%20as%20erythema%20infectiosum%2C%20as%20a%20viral%20infection%20caused%20by%20human%20parvovirus%20B19.%20It%20primarily%20affects%20children%20and%20is%20spread%20through%20respiratory%20droplets%20when%20an%20infected%20person%20coughs%20or%20sneezes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recognizable%20symptom%20is%20a%20characteristic%20bright-red%20rash%20on%20the%20cheeks%2C%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bslapped%20cheek%20syndrome.%26quot%3B%20This%20rash%20can%20then%20spread%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20body%20and%20may%20be%20accompanied%20by%20additional%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20social%20media%20users%20asked%20the%20doctor%20why%20he%20did%20not%20consult%20a%20general%20practitioner%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20do%20not%20understand%20that%20most%20times%2C%20nowadays%2C%20a%20'GP'%20is%20not%20the%20GP%20that%20we%20expect%20these%20days.%20Half%20my%20time%20in%20outpatient%20is%20spent%20deprescribing%20medications%20unnecessarily%20given%20by%20so-called%20GPs%20and%20specialists.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20virtue%20signal%20on%20social%20media%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20far%20different.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20maid's%20diagnosis%20was%20extremely%20valuable%20and%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20take%20a%20day%20off%20to%20see%20a%20'GP'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Dr%20Philips%20emerged%20as%20a%20hero%20when%20he%20acted%20swiftly%20to%20save%20a%20man's%20life%20in%20mid-air%20on%20an%20Akasa%20Air%20flight%20from%20Kochi%20to%20Mumbai.%20He%20is%20also%20known%20for%20his%20research%20efforts%20aimed%20at%20dispelling%20myths%20surrounding%20alternative%20medicine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718292660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fq2mdlk7o_doctor-generic_625x300_13_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fdoctor-stumped-by-family-members-illness-maid-diagnoses-it-in-10-seconds-5883795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20Dr%20Philips%20continued%20his%20research%20by%20consulting%20medical%20texts%2C%20his%20maid%20unexpectedly%20offered%20valuable%20insight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fdoctor-stumped-by-family-members-illness-maid-diagnoses-it-in-10-seconds-5883795%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fdoctor-stumped-by-family-members-illness-maid-diagnoses-it-in-10-seconds-5883795%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fdoctor-stumped-by-family-members-illness-maid-diagnoses-it-in-10-seconds-5883795%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kenyan%20policeman%20shoots%20magistrate%20in%20open%20court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718292216000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F00e2%2Flive%2Faa12be10-298c-11ef-9030-93974cf26f48.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc722j8d94vno%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20officer%20is%20said%