to%20not%20bring%20them%20under%20either%20female%20or%20male%20category%20for%20education%20and%20employment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20V%20Bhavani%20Subbaroyan%20in%20an%20order%20passed%20on%20June%2012%2C%202024%20said%20in%20'every%20employment%20and%20educational%20avenues%2C'%20the%20government%20shall%20prescribe%20separate%20norms%20for%20transgenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20shall%20direct%20all%20the%20state%20recruiting%20agencies%20to%20specify%20transgender%20as%20a%20special%20category%20and%20prescribe%20separate%20norms%20for%20their%20cut-off%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20relaxation%20open%20to%20other%20special%20categories%20shall%20also%20be%20extended%20to%20transgenders%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20caste%2C%20in%20future%20employment%20and%20educational%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transgender%20at%20no%20point%20of%20time%20in%20future%20shall%20be%20brought%20under%20male%20or%20female%20categories%2C%20the%20judge%20made%20it%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20a%20petition%20from%20R%20Anushri%2C%20a%20transgender%20who%20was%20denied%20the%20opportunity%20from%20being%20considered%20for%20combined%20civil%20service%20examination%20for%20the%20year%202017-18%20which%20were%20for%20non-interview%20post%20group-II%20A%20services%20under%20various%20categories%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20since%20the%20petitioner%20has%20scored%20the%20eligible%20cut-off%20mark%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20shall%20permit%20the%20petitioner%20to%20upload%20documents%20for%20certificate%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20said%20the%20petitioner%20has%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20scheduled%20caste%20woman%20category%20and%20denied%20permission%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(TNPSC)%20to%20upload%20her%20certificate%20for%20verification%20as%20she%20had%20scored%20less%20than%20the%20cut-off%20prescribed%20for%20scheduled%20caste%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETNPSC's%20approach%20is%20unsustainable%20and%20it%20had%20not%20categorised%20transgenders%20as%20a%20special%20category.%20Also%2C%20bringing%20the%20petitioner%20under%20woman%20category%20went%20against%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20Madras%20High%20court%2C%20the%20judge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20has%20clearly%20said%20that%20the%20transgenders%20should%20be%20treated%20as%20unique%20and%20they%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20one%20among%20the%20male%20or%20female.%20In%20fact%2C%20when%20Punjab%20had%20placed%20all%20the%20transgenders%20under%20male%20category%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20held%20such%20action%20as%20illegal%20and%20unsustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20transgenders%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20caste%20in%20which%20they%20were%20born%20and%20treated%20in%20the%20said%20category.%20This%20was%20of%20no%20use%20and%20detrimental%20to%20their%20development%2C%20the%20judge%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20order%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20though%20the%20National%20Legal%20Service%20Authority%20case%20was%20decided%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20early%20as%20April%2015%2C%202014%2C%20still%2C%20neither%20the%20state%20government%2C%20nor%20the%20central%20government%20has%20come%20forward%20to%20'formulate%20a%20uniform%20mode%20of%20employment%20opportunities'%20to%20be%20provided%20for%20the%20transgenders.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718286060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F48akc36g_india-pride-paradelgbtq650_625x300_07_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftreat-transgenders-as-special-category-for-employment-education-high-court-5882264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Holding%20that%20the%20transgenders%20should%20be%20treated%20only%20as%20a%20special%20category%20irrespective%20of%20their%20caste%2C%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20has%20directed%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20to%20not%20bring%20them%20under%20either%20female%20or%20male%20category%20for%20education%20and%20employment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftreat-transgenders-as-special-category-for-employment-education-high-court-5882264%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftreat-transgenders-as-special-category-for-employment-education-high-court-5882264%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftreat-transgenders-as-special-category-for-employment-education-high-court-5882264%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ajit%20Doval%20To%20Take%20Charge%20Of%20National%20Security%20A%20Third%20Time%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20historic%20third%20term%2C%20has%20reposed%20faith%20again%20in%20his%20most%20trusted%20advisers%20--%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20PK%20Mishra.%C2%A0%20Mr%20Doval%2C%2079%2C%20has%20been%20reappointed%20National%20Security%20Adviser.%20Mr%20Mishra%20retains%20his%20position%20as%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval%20was%20appointed%20the%20NSA%20a%20decade%20ago%20when%20PM%20Modi%20swept%20to%20power%20with%20a%20massive%20mandate.%20He%20became%20the%20country's%20key%20interlocutor%20for%20neighbouring%20countries.%20He%20also%20handled%20the%20external%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20the%20Research%20and%20Analysis%20Wing%20(RAW).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20was%20inevitable%2C%20given%20Mr%20Doval's%20formidable%20reputation%20as%20the%20country's%20premier%20security%20expert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20policeman%20to%20be%20decorated%20with%20the%20country's%20second-highest%20peacetime%20gallantry%20award%2C%20Kirti%20Chakra%2C%20Mr%20Doval%20retired%20as%20Director%20of%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20in%202005.%C2%A0%20His%20field%20experience%20is%20staggering%2C%20making%20him%20a%20legend%20in%20the%20country's%20intelligence%20circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20part%20of%20several%20counter-terrorism%20operations%20in%20Mizoram%2C%20Punjab%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20He%20infiltrated%20Amritsar's%20Golden%20Temple%20during%20the%20Operation%20Black%20Thunder%20of%201988%2C%20posing%20as%20a%20Pakistani%20agent%20and%20came%20back%20with%20vital%20intel%20on%20the%20terrorists%20holed%20up%20inside.%20He%20was%20among%20the%20officers%20who%20negotiated%20the%20release%20of%20the%20passengers%20of%20the%20hijacked%20plane%20IC-814.%20He%20also%20did%20a%20six-year%20stint%20in%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20appointment%20as%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Policy%20Group%20--%20meant%20for%20inter-ministerial%20coordination%20and%20integration%20of%20inputs%20--%20in%202018%20made%20him%20the%20most%20powerful%20bureaucrat%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20group%20includes%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%20vice%20chairman%2C%20the%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20the%20three%20military%20chiefs%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20governor%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%2C%20home%20secretary%2C%20finance%20secretary%20and%20the%20defence%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20Mr%20Doval%20has%20been%20the%20Centre's%20pointsperson%20in%20countering%20the%20face-off%20with%20China%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20Doklam.%20He%20is%20also%20India's%20special%20representative%20for%20resolving%20the%20boundary%20issue%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20plenty%20on%20the%20NSA's%20desk%20as%20he%20resumes%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Doval's%20reappointment%20comes%20as%20the%20Centre%20confronts%20a%20series%20of%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20following%20the%20Union%20Territory's%20first%20election%20after%20the%20scrapping%20of%20Article%20370%20in%202019.%20A%20record%20number%20of%20people%20voted%20in%20the%20recent%20general%20election%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20boycott%20call%20in%20Kashmir%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718285700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fu3mcatlg_ajit-dovals-_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-doval-to-take-charge-of-national-security-a-third-time-5883023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20historic%20third%20term%2C%20has%20reposed%20faith%20again%20his%20most%20trusted%20advisors%20--%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20PK%20Mishra.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-doval-to-take-charge-of-national-security-a-third-time-5883023%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-doval-to-take-charge-of-national-security-a-third-time-5883023%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-doval-to-take-charge-of-national-security-a-third-time-5883023%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTold%20Them%20He%20Has%20Tattoo%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20A%20Father%20Identified%20Kuwait%20Fire%20Victim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPradeep%2C%20father%20of%2027-year-old%20Srihari%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20building%20that%20caught%20fire%20in%20Kuwait%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%2049%20deaths%2C%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20body%20of%20his%20son%20only%20from%20the%20tattoo%20on%20his%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPradeep%20said%20he%20was%20called%20by%20the%20authorities%20to%20identify%20his%20son's%20body%20kept%20in%20a%20hospital%20mortuary.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20there%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20the%20face%20was%20completely%20swollen%20and%20the%20nose%20was%20covered%20with%20soot.%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20identify%20him.%20I%20just%20could%20not...%20Then%20I%20told%20them%20that%20he%20had%20a%20tattoo%20on%20his%20hand.%20Based%20on%20that%20he%20was%20identified%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20sobbing%20Pradeep%20told%20a%20Malayalam%20news%20channel%20in%20Kuwait%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrihari%20had%20returned%20to%20Kuwait%20from%20Kerala%20on%20June%205%20and%20both%20father%20and%20son%20worked%20for%20the%20same%20company.%20Pradeep%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Kuwait%20for%20eight%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20a%20friend%20of%20the%20family%20told%20reporters%20Srihari%20left%20for%20Kuwait%20recently.%20%26quot%3BBarely%20a%20week%20later%2C%20news%20of%20his%20death%20reached%20here.%20We%20learned%20about%20it%20last%20afternoon.%20His%20father%20informed%20the%20family%20as%20there%20were%20news%20reports%20on%20TV%20about%20the%20tragedy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20family%20friend%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Srihari%20was%20working%20in%20a%20supermarket%20in%20Kuwait%20until%20he%20could%20find%20a%20job%20related%20to%20his%20field%20of%20study%2C%20mechanical%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20father%20is%20trying%20to%20return%20to%20Kerala%20by%20today%2C%20and%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20bring%20back%20his%20body%20by%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20Centre%20and%20state%20governments%20nor%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Kuwait%20have%20officially%20confirmed%20the%20identities%20of%20the%20Indians%20who%20perished%20in%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Kuwaiti%20authorities%2C%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20a%20building%20in%20the%20southern%20city%20of%20Mangaf%2C%20in%20which%2049%20foreign%20workers%2C%20including%20around%2040%20Indians%2C%20were%20killed%2C%20and%2050%20others%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20started%20in%20the%20kitchen%20of%20the%20seven-storey%20building%20housing%20195%20migrant%20workers%20in%20Mangaf%20in%20the%20Ahmadi%20Governorate%20early%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20erupted%20just%20after%204%20am%20when%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20196%20all-male%20residents%20of%20the%20building%20were%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20resulted%20in%20huge%2C%20thick%20clouds%20of%20black%20smoke%20that%20led%20to%20most%20of%20the%20victims%20suffocating%20to%20death%2C%20according%20to%20officials%20from%20the%20Kuwait%20Interior%20Ministry%20and%20the%20fire%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718285580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjn88lc_kuwait-fire-_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftold-them-he-has-tattoo-how-a-father-identified-kuwait-fire-victim-5883013%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pradeep%2C%20father%20of%2027-year-old%20Srihari%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20building%20that%20caught%20fire%20in%20Kuwait%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%2049%20deaths%2C%20was%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20body%20of%20his%20son%20only%20from%20the%20tattoo%20on%20his%20hand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftold-them-he-has-tattoo-how-a-father-identified-kuwait-fire-victim-5883013%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftold-them-he-has-tattoo-how-a-father-identified-kuwait-fire-victim-5883013%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftold-them-he-has-tattoo-how-a-father-identified-kuwait-fire-victim-5883013%2Famp%