larities%20and%20corruption%20within%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Ffaqs-on-neet-ug-nta-answers-questions-on-paper-leak-and-cheating-in-medical-entrance-exam-5875078%5C%22%3ENational%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20holds%20these%20exams%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EHere%20is%20a%20look%20at%20what%20has%20happened%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EInflated%20marks%20and%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0The%20controversy%20began%20after%20marksheets%20of%20some%20successful%20candidates%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%20Users%20who%20posted%20these%20images%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20record%2067%20candidates%20secured%20the%20top%20rank%20with%20perfect%20score.%20Of%20these%2C%20around%20six%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%20from%20the%20same%20centre.%20Students%20have%20been%20alleging%20the%20marks%20have%20been%20randomly%20reduced%20or%20increased%20for%20several%20candidates%2C%20affecting%20their%20ranks.%20There%20have%20been%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak%20too.%20The%20Economic%20Offences%20Unit%20of%20Bihar%20Police%20had%20last%20month%20said%20that%20its%20investigation%20has%20revealed%20that%20the%20question%20papers%20and%20answers%20for%20NEET-UG%20were%20provided%20to%20approximately%2035%20aspirants%20before%20the%20May%205%20exam.%20Thirteen%20individuals%20have%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20In%20total%2C%201%2C563%20students%20received%20the%20grace%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fneet-ug-2024-result-row-top-rankers-reduced-to-61-as-grace-marks-withdrawn-5882844%5C%22%3ENEET%20UG%20Result%202024%3A%20Top%20Rankers%20Reduced%20To%2061%20As%20Grace%20Marks%20Withdrawn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%201%2C563%20students%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fno-student-will-face-any-disadvantage-union-minister-dharmendra-pradhan-on-neet-row-5880050%5C%22%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20aspirants%20at%20some%20centres%20were%20given%20the%20wrong%20set%20of%20papers.%20These%20students%20appeared%20for%20exam%20at%20six%20centres%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Surat%20and%20Chandigarh.%20These%20students%20(totalling%201%2C563)%20claimed%20that%20did%20not%20get%20the%20full%203%20hours%20and%2020%20minutes%20to%20write%20the%20exam%20due%20to%20administrative%20reasons%2C%20including%20the%20distribution%20of%20the%20wrong%20question%20paper%2C%20torn%20OMR%20sheets%2C%20or%20delay%20in%20the%20distribution%20of%20OMR%20sheets.%20A%20committee%20formed%20by%20the%20NTA%20investigated%20the%20matter%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20formula%20devised%20and%20adopted%20by%20the%20apex%20court%20in%20a%202018%20judgement%2C%20to%20address%20the%20loss%20of%20time%20faced%20by%20candidates.%20The%20loss%20of%20time%20was%20ascertained%20and%20such%20candidates%20were%20compensated%20with%20grace%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20NTA%20said%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0As%20the%20controversy%20blew%20up%2C%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20came%20out%20with%20a%20statement%20maintaining%20that%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20not%20been%20compromised.%20It%20said%20that%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20top%20scorers%20reflects%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20competitiveness%20of%20the%20exam%20and%20improvement%20in%20performance%20standards.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20grace%20marks%20were%20awarded%20to%201%2C563%20candidates%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20time%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20approved%20formula.%20Out%20of%20the%2067%20candidates%20who%20got%20720%20out%20of%20720%20marks%2C%2044%20are%20on%20account%20of%20the%20revision%20in%20one%20answer%20key%20of%20Physics%2C%20and%20six%20are%20on%20account%20of%20compensatory%20marks%20for%20loss%20of%20time.%20This%20adjustment%20aimed%20to%20address%20inconsistencies%20in%20NCERT%20textbooks%2C%20ensuring%20candidates%20were%20not%20disadvantaged%20by%20factual%20discrepancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEducation%20Ministry%20denies%20paper%20leak%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0The%20ministry%20has%20set%20up%20a%20four-member%20expert%20panel%20headed%20by%20former%20UPSC%20chairman%20to%20review%20the%20entire%20matter.%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20the%20allegations%20saying%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20of%20paper%20leak%20and%20claims%20of%20corruption%20in%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPolitics%20over%20NEET%20controversy%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0The%20matter%20has%20also%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20Congress%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20Supreme%20Court-monitored%20probe%20into%20the%20NEET%20exam%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20anger%20in%20the%20country%20over%20the%20matter%20will%20%26quot%3Breverberate%20inside%20Parliament%20as%20well%26quot%3B.%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20accused%20the%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20of%20defending%20NTA%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20Bihar%20Police%20investigation%20has%20found%20a%20paper%20leak.%20%C2%A0The%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20sought%20immediate%20cancellation%20of%20the%20exam%2C%20alleging%20that%20its%20results%20have%20caused%20injustice%20to%20the%20students%20from%20the%20state.%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20said%20the%20trends%20from%20the%20latest%20NEET%20results%20have%20once%20again%20vindicated%20the%20DMK%20on%20its%20stand%20opposing%20the%20exam%20and%20reiterated%20that%20the%20entrance%20test%20goes%20against%20social%20justice%20and%20federalism.