%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhappy-days-star-henry-winkler-aka-the-fonz-praises-dublin-fire-service-after-blaze-at-his-hotel-13152556%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhappy-days-star-henry-winkler-aka-the-fonz-praises-dublin-fire-service-after-blaze-at-his-hotel-13152556%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Of%20Pir%20Panjal%2C%20Terror's%20New%20Address%20In%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETerror%20has%20got%20a%20new%20address%20-%20south%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Delhi%20is%20worried%20how%20the%20theatre%20of%20terror%20has%20shifted%20from%20the%20north%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20to%20the%20south%20of%20Pir%20Panjal%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20learnt%20that%20an%20urgent%20meeting%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20was%20called%20earlier%20this%20week%20to%20take%20stock%20of%20these%20terror%20attacks.%20They%20gave%20top%20priority%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20pilgrims%20in%20the%20Amarnath%20yatra%2C%20which%20will%20start%20on%20June%2029%20and%20end%20on%20August%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForces%20had%20thinned%20down%20over%20the%20years%20as%20the%20area%20had%20become%20relatively%20peaceful.%20The%20terrain%20also%20adds%20to%20the%20movement%20of%20terrorists%20and%20that's%20why%20incidents%20are%20going%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20North%20Block%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20%C2%A0this%20week%2C%20a%20joint%20audit%20was%20conducted%20by%20security%20and%20intelligence%20agencies%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20and%20gaps%20were%20noted.%20%26quot%3BThese%20gaps%20have%20been%20filled%2C%20and%20area%20domination%20exercises%20are%20being%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20officer%20on%20the%20field%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20army%20has%20so%20far%20maintained%20that%20no%20infiltration%20happened%20last%20year.%20But%20the%20four%20recent%20encounters%20have%20negated%20their%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntelligence%20sources%20said%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20exploit%20communal%20fault%20lines%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%20which%20is%20why%20terrorists%20have%20been%20carrying%20out%20targetted%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTargeting%20of%20pilgrims%20was%20done%20knowing%20fully%20well%20that%20it%20may%20cause%20a%20flare-up%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20in%20North%20Block%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20has%20just%20conducted%20peaceful%20elections%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPakistan%20obviously%20does%20not%20want%20this%20narrative%20to%20gain%20momentum%20and%20that's%20why%20they%20have%20been%20pushing%20terrorists%20to%20the%20Jammu%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said%2C%20adding%20Pakistan%20wants%20to%20demolish%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20total%20normalcy%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20local%20(terror)%20recruitments%20have%20come%20down%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20been%20sending%20terrorists%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20RR%20Swain%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20four%20%C2%A0terror%20attacks%20indicate%20that%20this%20proxy%20war%20will%20continue%20to%20simmer%20at%20varying%20degrees%20of%20intensity%20and%20the%20involvement%20of%20new%20groups%20-%20whether%20it%20is%20Kashmir%20Tigers%20or%20the%20Resistance%20Front%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20official%20who%20is%20on%20the%20field%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718281920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Fhg7j3v08_pir-panjal-range_625x300_23_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsouth-of-pir-panjal-terrors-new-address-in-jammu-and-kashmir-5882608%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Terror%20has%20got%20a%20new%20address%20-%20south%20of%20Pir%