2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352048%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESunita%20harvests%20at%20least%205%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20week.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ingenious%20gardeners%20share%20gardening%20tips%20for%20creating%20a%20vertical%20garden%20using%20PVC%20pipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.Take%20a%20five-foot%20pipe%20and%20cut%20it%20into%20sections%20according%20to%20the%20number%20of%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20you%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Avoid%20drilling%20an%20excessive%20number%20of%20holes%20in%20the%20pipe.%20Maintain%20a%20distance%20of%2018%20inches%20between%20holes%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20gap%20of%20nine%20inches%20on%20the%20opposite%20side%20of%20the%20pipe.%20In%20total%2C%20there%20should%20be%20five%20evenly%20spaced%20holes%20along%20a%20six-foot%20pipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Close%20the%20extra%20holes%2C%20if%20any%2C%20using%20a%20hot%20air%20gun.%20Do%20not%20forget%20to%20tape%20the%20extra%20holes%20to%20prevent%20water%20leakage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Fill%20three-fourth%20part%20of%20the%20pipe%20with%20soil%20and%20plant%20the%20seed%20or%20sapling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Add%20a%20mixture%20of%20vermicompost%20or%20any%20other%20organic%20fertiliser%20to%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E6.%20Create%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20soil%20and%20fill%20it%20with%20sand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E7.%20Water%20the%20sand%20so%20that%20it%20stays%20wet%20and%20the%20moisture%20reaches%20the%20bottom%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E8.%20There%20is%20no%20need%20to%20change%20the%20soil%20for%20the%20next%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E9.%20New%20saplings%20or%20seeds%20can%20be%20planted%20by%20simply%20making%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E10.%20Neem%20water%20can%20be%20used%20to%20avoid%20pests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGardening%20in%20two%20five-foot%20PVC%20pipes%20typically%20costs%20around%20Rs%201%2C000.%20With%20this%20setup%2C%20you%20can%20cultivate%20four%20to%20five%20varieties%20of%20vegetables%2C%20ranging%20from%20leafy%20greens%20to%20tubers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20gardening!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717507364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fpvc-pipe-gardening-1-1717506324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352038%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gardeners%20Mithilesh%20Kumar%20Singh%20and%20Sunita%20Prasad%20show%20how%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20even%20in%20small%20spaces.%20Here's%20how%20they%20innovate%20using%20PVC%20pipes%20to%20grow%20mini-gardens%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%228%20Best%20Vada%20Pav%20Spots%20in%20Mumbai%20For%20That%20Authentic%20Taste%3B%20Bookmark%20Now!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThis%3Cem%3E%20desi%3C%2Fem%3E%20snack%20has%20found%20its%20ranks%20among%20the%20%E2%80%98best%20sandwiches%20in%20the%20world%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20the%20monsoon%20season%E2%80%99s%20perfect%20companion%2C%20a%20quick%20fix%20for%20a%20bad%20day%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20best%20time%20machines%20ever%20made%20%E2%80%94%20it%20immediately%20transports%20you%20back%20to%20your%20college%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20face%20it%3A%20the%20emotional%20implications%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303199%2Fmumbai-duo-started-shree-krishna-vada-pav-food-chain-in-london-turned-millionaires-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20many.%20And%20this%20deep-fried%20potato%20dumpling%20hugged%20