20I%20want%20one%20more.%20Probably%20the%20best%20lunch%20you%20can%20buy%20in%20Rs%2015!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717494416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FClassic-Vada-Pav-1-1716555449.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Vada%20pav'%2C%20the%20beloved%20Indian%20snack%2C%20never%20fails%20to%20evoke%20nostalgia%20and%20emotional%20connections.%20Mumbai%20boasts%20iconic%20spots%20like%20Aram%2C%20Ashok%20Vaidya%20Vada%20Pav%2C%20Swati%20Snacks%2C%20and%20more%2C%20each%20offering%20unique%20renditions%20of%20this%20culinary%20classic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351102%2Fbest-vada-pav-places-mumbai-ashok-vaidya-aram-shankar-gajanan-swati-snacks-jai-maharashtra-shivaji-park%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Use%20Cardboard%20Boxes%20to%20Protect%20Your%20Plants%20From%20The%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20you%20receive%20a%20package%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20the%20cardboard%20waste%3F%20In%20India%2C%20households%2C%20itinerant%20waste%20merchants%2C%20and%20garbage%20collectors%20jointly%20recover%202.4%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0921344915300082%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHouseholds%252C%2520itinerant%2520waste%2520merchants%2520and%2Ctonnes%2520of%2520plastic%252C%2520more%2520than1.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4.3%20million%20tonnes%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20cardboard%20and%20mixed%20paper%20annually.%20Overall%2C%2030%E2%80%9360%20percent%20of%20all%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20is%20recycled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata-based%20Krishna%20Khuku%20ha