tterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fscuzo2-1717419614-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351924%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EScuzo%20specialises%20in%20ice%20popsicles%20and%20gelato%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20rarely%20had%20electricity%20growing%20up%20as%20we%20used%20to%20stay%20in%20Naxal%20areas.%20It%20was%20a%20precarious%20situation%20and%20as%20safety%20itself%20was%20such%20a%20big%20issue%2C%20lack%20of%20electricity%20didn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20be%20a%20big%20problem%20then.%20The%20first%20time%20we%20had%20uninterrupted%20electricity%20was%20when%20I%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gagan%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20they%20had%20a%20happy%20childhood%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20as%20they%20had%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20Delhi%2C%20he%20became%20a%20shift%20manager%20at%20Pizza%20Hut%20in%202006.%20This%20was%20quickly%20followed%20by%20the%20restaurant%20general%20manager%20post%20in%202008%2C%20at%20the%20age%20of%2021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20when%20he%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20best%20manager%2C%20the%20video%20was%20circulated%20to%20Pizza%20Hut%20stores%20across%20the%20world%2C%20which%20led%20to%20his%20next%20stint%20at%20one%20of%20its%20centres%20in%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20Kandahar%20airfield.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handling%20Pizza%20Hut%2C%20Burger%20King%2C%20Kentucky%20Fried%20Chicken%20(KFC)%20stores%20at%20Kandahar%20as%20a%20general%20manager%20for%202.5%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20stint%20propelled%20his%20career%2C%20leading%20to%20his%20next%20stint%20at%20Gloria%20Jeans%20coffee%20in%20Dubai.%20He%20returned%20to%20India%20to%20build%20a%20company%20called%20Honey%20Hut%2C%20which%20gave%20him%20a%20ground%20up%20idea%C2%A0into%20franchising.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20build%20their%20franchise%20vertically.%20I%20created%2015%20stores%20in%20two%20years%20and%20developed%20their%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%20(SOPs)%2C%20how%20to%20work%2C%20what%20to%20do%20and%20what%20not%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20here%20on%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20other%20franchising%20verticals%20at%20the%20Chocolate%20Room%20and%20Rasna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20created%20the%20food%20and%20beverage%20verticals%20at%20Rasna%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20make%20cafes.%20We%20opened%20over%2070%20stores%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20creating%20brands%20for%20others%2C%20Gagan%20desired%20to%20create%20his%20own%20brand.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20being%20in%20a%20high%20position%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20make%20my%20own%20decisions.%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20my%20own%20brand%20where%20I%20could%20have%20the%20liberty%20to%20do%20whatever%20I%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20a%20trip%20down%20memory%20lane%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20childhood%20memories%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20continuing%20craze%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250305%2Fbarath-jaiyanth-food-truck-ice-cream-startup-tickle-truck-chenna-besant-nagar-beach-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopsicle%20sticks%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20world%2C%20led%20to%20an%20idea%20of%20creating%20a%20%E2%80%98live%E2%80%99%20popsicle%20brand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1n_uV4y2EO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1n_uV4y2EO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC1n_uV4y2EO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20%40scuzo_thrissur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20pizzas%20were%20being%20made%20in%20front%20of%20customers%2C%20why%20not%20popsicles%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20US%2C%20there%20are%20many%20brands%20selling%20popsicle%20sticks.%20In%20India%20though%2C%20I%20found%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20being%20sold%20on%20the%20streets.%20I%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20making%20it%20an%20immersive%20experience%2C%20taking%20people%20down%20the%20memory%20lane%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20implanted%20in%20his%20mind%20since%202016-17%20and%20Gagan%20worked%20on%20it%20for%20over%20four%20years%20before%20launching%20the%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20and%20the%20lockdown%20gave%20him%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20experiment%20and%20create%20these%20popsicles.%20In%20an%20attempt%20to%20provide%20a%20healthier%20alternative%20to%20ice-cream%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20chefs%20to%20create%20recipes%20made%20out%20of%20fruits.%20He%20also%20got%20his%20team%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20developing%20a%20popsicle%20machine%20that%20would%20freeze%20them%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes.%20Months%20of%20trials%20and%20four%20prototypes%20later%2C%20he%20had%20the%20perfect%20machine%20ready%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Cfreezes%20a%20popsicle%20within%207%20to%208%20minutes%20in%20front%20of%20you%20with%20a%20temperature%20of%20minus%2031%20degrees%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20experience%20in%20the%20franchising%20business%20and%20QSR%20(Quick%20Service%20Restaurant)%20led%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20string%20of%20processes%20that%20can%20easily%20be%20replicated%20across%20stores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvesting%20Rs%2070%20lakh%20of%20his%20savings%2C%20Gagan%20started%20the%20first%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%20store%20in%20Netaji%20Subhash%20Place%2C%20Pitampura%2C%20New%20Delhi%20in%20November%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20that%20just%20popsicles%20might%20not%20work%2C%20he%20also%20developed%20gelato%2C%20an%20Italian%20frozen%20dessert%2C%20in%20a%20manufacturing%20unit.%20In%20order%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20wider%20audience%2C%20the%20dessert%20cafe%20serves%20waffles%2C%20milkshakes%2C%20hot%20beverages%2C%20sundaes%20in%20addition%20to%20popsicles%20and%20gelato.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20had%20a%20great%20response%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founder%2C%20with%20people%20enquiring%20for%20franchisees%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20itself.%20The%20first%20franchise%20store%20was%20opened%20in%20March%202021.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Scuzo%20has%2030%20stores%20in%2025%20cities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20of%20which%2027%20are%20franchisees%20and%203%20are%20company-owned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273408%2Fskippi-ice-popsicles-ravi-anuja-kabra-win-million-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopsicles%20start%20at%20Rs%2065%20%3C%2Fa%3Ea%20piece%20while%20the%20gelato%20starts%20at%20Rs%20110.%20Their%20bestseller%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Echatpata%20jamun%20%3C%2Fem%3Epopsicle%3Cem%3E.%20%3C%2Fem%3EGagan%20shares%20that%20the%20popsicles%20are%20made%20from%20%E2%80%98100%20percent%20fruit%E2%80%99.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20are%20served%20with%20edible%20rice%20straws.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20has%20been%20far%20from%20smooth%20as%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20COVID-19%20brought%20a%20halt%20to%20his%20growth.%20The%20first%20store%2C%20which%20was%20in%20a%20mall%2C%20had%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20and%20moved%20to%20Noida.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivery%20too%2C%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%20according%20to%20Gagan.%20Most%20food%20delivery%20companies%20don%E2%80%99t%20provide%20the%20cooling%20pouch%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20just%205%20percent%20of%20sales%20from%20online%20channels.%20To%20combat%20this%2C%20Gagan%20hopes%20to%20start%20his%20own%20delivery%20service%20to%20ensure%20proper%20delivery%20of%20the%20popsicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20was%20his%20happiest%20moment%3F%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20very%20proud%20of%20me%20because%20I%20achieved%20so%20much%20without%20taking%20a%20single%20rupee%20from%20him.%20He%20passed%20away%20in%202021%2C%20but%20he%20got%20to%20see%20all%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Image%20Courtesy%3A%20Gagan%20Anand%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717422447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-06-03-at-18.45.33-min-1717420586.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351903%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gagan%20Anand%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20when%20he%20was%2017%20and%20picked%20up%20a%20job%20at%20Pizza%20Hut.%20Starting%20with%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%201500%2C%20he%20now%20runs%20a%20dessert%20cafe%20called%20Scuzo%20Ice-O-Magic%2C%20which%20serves%20popsicles%20and%20gelato.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20his%20entrepreneurial%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351903%2Fice-popsicle-startup-scuzo-chai-delhi-ncr-fruit-gelatos-live-dessert-cafe-gagan-anand%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Doctor%20Returned%20From%20The%20UK%20%26amp%3B%20Inspired%202.5%20Million%20Indians%20to%20Become%20Future%20Organ%20Donors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20year%20was%201996.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Sunil%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20voice%20softens%20as%20he%20narrates%20a%20life%20changing%20incident%20that%20happened%20back%20then.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2070-year-old%20urologist%20and%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%20was%20about%20to%20perform%20one%20of%20his%20first%20few%20%E2%80%98deceased%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310277%2Fabhinav-pangtey-shares-myths-about-organ-donation-india-world-transplant-games%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorgan%20donations%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20on%20a%2012-year-old%20boy%20who%20died%20of%20a%20cobra%20bite.%20The%20surgery%20was%20scheduled%20at%20the%20Sri%20Ramachandra%20Medical%20College%20and%20Research%20Institute%20(SRMC%20%26amp%3B%20RI)%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20explains%20how%20after%20the%20initial%20treatment%20failed%2C%20the%20young%20child%20was%20declared%20brain%20dead%20at%20the%20hospital.%20The%20doctors%20there%20waited%20for%20five%20days%20for%20him%20to%20recover%2C%20but%20he%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20did%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20hesitantly%20approached%20the%20grief-stricken%20father%20and%20asked%20him%20whether%20he%20would%20donate%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20organs%2C%20which%20he%20consented%20to.%20Two%20kidneys%2C%20a%20heart%20and%20two%20corneas%20were%20harvested%20and%20transplanted%20in%20five%20individuals%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139488%2Forgan-donation-india-youth-awareness-increase%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egiving%20them%20the%20gift%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20the%20hospital%20famous%20as%20it%20was%20only%20the%20fourth%20hospital%20to%20perform%20such%20a%20procedure%20in%20the%20country.%20This%20unique%20case%20of%20organ%20donation%20from%20a%20snake%20bite%20victim%20was%20published%20in%20an%20international%20journal%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%20began%20Dr%20Shroff%E2%80%99s%20dedicated%20mission%20to%20promote%20deceased%20organ%20donation%20and%20transplantation%20in%20India.%20To%20facilitate%20his%20mission%2C%20he%20established%20the%20not-for-profit%20MOHAN%20(Multi%20Organ%20Harvesting%20Aid%20Network)%20Foundation%20in%201997.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20is%20a%20senior%20consultant%20of%20urology%20and%20transplantation%20at%20the%20Madras%20Medical%20Mission%20Hospital%20in%20Chennai.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20managing%20trustee%20of%20MOHAN%20Foundation.%20Notably%2C%20he%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20surgeon%20to%20perform%20a%20successful%20kidney%20transplant%20on%20an%20HIV%20positive%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20with%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%2C%2010%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20suffer%20from%20end-stage%20organ%20failure%20every%20year.%20Only%2016%2C041%20receive%20live-saving%20organs%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20755px)%20100vw%2C%20755px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22755%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20in%201997%2C%20Chennai.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294.jpg%20755w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294-500x279.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351936%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20in%201997%2C%20Chennai.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20all%20started%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20was%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20by%20his%20grandparents%20in%20Sahibganj%2C%20a%20small%20railway%20town%20in%20Bihar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20describes%20himself%20as%20a%20fearless%2C%20risk-taker%20and%20a%20free-spirited%20child.%20%E2%80%9CI%20once%20saved%20a%20friend%20who%20was%20drowning%20in%20the%20Ganga%20river.%20Also%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20dare%20from%20my%20brother%2C%20I%20jumped%20from%20the%20first%20floor.%20I%20am%20surprised%20I%20survived!%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140465%2Fmumbai-schools-spread-organ-donation-awareness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20qualities%20in%20me%20shaped%20my%20life%20and%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20he%20got%20married%20and%20became%20a%20father%2C%20he%20found%20that%20he%20could%20not%20support%20his%20family%20as%20doctors%20did%20not%20get%20paid%20well%20in%20India%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20left%20for%20the%20UK%20where%20he%20lived%20for%2012%20years%20and%20completed%20his%20Fellowship%20of%20the%20Royal%20College%20of%20Surgeons%20(FRCS)%20and%20Diploma%20in%20Urology%20in%20the%20UK%20in%201990.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20promised%20my%20mother%20I%20would%20return%20to%20India.%20Also%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20belonging%20to%20India%20though%20I%20was%20well-settled%20in%20the%20UK.%20My%20colleagues%20would%20often%20tease%20me%20about%20the%20kidney%20transplant%20scandals%20in%20India.%20That%20hurt%20my%20feelings%20as%20when%20you%20are%20abroad%2C%20you%20become%20the%20representative%20of%20your%20country.%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20back%20home%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270029%2Findia-longest-coma-survivor-dr-jaideep-sharma-organ-donation-register%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edo%20something%20to%20change%20the%20situation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20I%20returned%20in%201995%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201784px)%20100vw%2C%201784px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221784%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Receiving%20his%20PG%20degree%20in%20the%20UK.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391.jpg%201784w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391-300x198.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391-500x331.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391-768x508.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391-1536x1016.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FReceiving-postgraduate-degree-in-urology-and-transplantation-in-the-UK_11zon-1717420391-150x99.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351937%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221180%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReceiving%20his%20PG%20degree%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBoost%20for%20deceased%20organ%20donation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20opportune%20time%20to%20return.%20The%20government%20then%20had%20just%20passed%20the%20Transplantation%20of%20Human%20Organs%20%26amp%3B%20Tissues%20Act%20(THOTA)%2C%201994.%20The%20law%20accepted%20brain%20death%20as%20legal%20death%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20boost%20for%20deceased%20organ%20donation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311982%2Fmumbai-hansa-raghwani-fought-stage-four-cancer-chemotherapy-surgery-recovery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20natural%20cardiac%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20only%20a%20few%20organs%20and%20tissues%20can%20be%20donated%20(like%20the%20cornea%2C%20bones%2C%20skin%20and%20blood%20vessels)%2C%20but%20after%20a%20brain%20death%2C%20eight%20solid%20organs%2C%20including%20the%20vital%20organs%20like%20kidneys%2C%C2%A0heart%2C%C2%A0liver%C2%A0and%C2%A0lungs%2C%20and%20almost%2050%20tissues%2C%20can%20be%20donated%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Act%20also%20made%20commercial%20dealings%20in%20human%20organs%20a%20punishable%20offence.%20It%20is%20the%20toughest%20law%20in%20the%20world%20as%20far%20as%20organ%20donation%20is%20concerned.%20The%20number%20of%20scams%20in%20kidneys%20have%20come%20down%20considerably%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Shroff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%2C%20he%20became%20aware%20of%20the%20huge%20shortage%20of%20kidneys%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20see%20the%20agony%20and%20desperation%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20caregivers%20and%20family%20members%20when%20no%20suitable%20kidney%20donor%20was%20available%20in%20the%20family.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20have%20an%20alternative%20to%20%E2%80%98live%20donations%E2%80%99.%20The%20answer%20was%20deceased%20organ%20donation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20no%20support%20system%20or%20awareness%20in%20the%20country%20at%20that%20time.%20The%20doctors%20themselves%20felt%20that%20brain%20death%20was%20too%20complex%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20public.%20They%20did%20not%20feel%20that%20deceased%20organ%20transplantation%20was%20possible%20in%20India%2C%20he%20rues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Shroff%20speaking%20at%20a%20conference.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSpeaking-at-a-conference_11zon-1717421181-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351958%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Shroff%20speaking%20at%20a%20conference.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEstablishing%20MOHAN%20Foundation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20set%20up%20the%20not-for-profit%20MOHAN%20Foundation.%20It%20was%20meant%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F206018%2Fhow-to-donate-organs-body-in-india-process-rules-donation-eligibility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20raise%20awareness%20about%20brain%20death%20and%20deceased%20organ%20donation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20we%20soon%20realised%20that%20was%20not%20enough%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Shroff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20needed%20to%20train%20ICU%20doctors%20and%20nurses%20in%20identifying%20brain%20death%2C%20organ%20retrieval%2C%20counselling%20and%20support%20families%20at%20the%20time%20of%20their%20grief.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20we%20also%20had%20to%20put%20systems%20in%20place%20at%20hospitals%2C%20and%20sensitise%20not%20only%20the%20general%20public%20but%20also%20the%20medical%20fraternity%20on%20this%20topic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20focuses%20on%20deceased%20organ%20donation%20for%20two%20reasons.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20heart%2C%20lungs%2C%20pancreas%20and%20intestines%2C%20the%20organs%20have%20to%20come%20from%20a%20deceased%20person.%20Live%20donations%20can%20only%20take%20place%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20kidney%20and%20part%20of%20the%20liver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20deceased%20organ%20donation%20and%20transplantation%20is%20a%20complex%20process%20that%20needs%20coordination%20between%20multiple%20stakeholders%2C%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20used%20technology%20extensively.%20We%20have%20software%20that%20finds%20out%20which%20patient%20on%20the%20waiting%20list%20should%20be%20given%20the%20next%20available%20organ.%20We%20use%20apps%20to%20identify%20and%20certify%20brain%20death.%20We%20also%20use%20AI%20to%20predict%20organ%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Shroff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20counselled%20more%20than%2012%2C000%20families%20successfully%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208322%2Fbengaluru-teen-teacher-death-blood-donation-community-inspiring-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20donate%20the%20organs%20of%20their%20loved%20ones%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20declared%20brain-dead.%20The%20conversion%20rate%20of%20such%20cases%20is%20high%20at%2060-70%25.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20has%20sensitised%20over%20250%20million%20people%20on%20organ%20donation%20and%20trained%20around%204%2C000%20grief%20counsellors%20or%20transplant%20coordinators%20and%20more%20than%2061%2C000%20medical%20professionals%20on%20organ%20donation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20issued%20over%202.5%20million%20donor%20cards.%20It%20has%20a%20helpline%20number%3A%2018001037100%20where%20queries%20on%20kidney%2C%20liver%20and%20other%20transplants%20are%20answered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMOHAN%20Foundation%20has%20offices%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Imphal%2C%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20inked%20MoUs%20with%20nine%20state%20governments%2C%20including%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Manipur.%20In%202011%2C%20when%20the%20law%20was%20being%20amended%2C%20the%20foundation%20came%20up%20with%20several%20recommendations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20authorities%20ensure%20that%20hospitals%20have%20transplant%20coordinators%20before%20giving%20licences.%20Since%20April%202018%2C%20when%20a%20person%20applies%20for%20a%20driving%20licence%2C%20there%20is%20a%20pop-up%20from%20the%20transport%20authority%20asking%20whether%20he%20or%20she%20would%20like%20to%20pledge%20organs.%20The%20ICU%20doctors%20are%20also%20morally%20obligated%20to%20ask%20for%20organs%20from%20the%20family%20in%20case%20of%20a%20brain%20death.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20team.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127-300x199.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127-500x332.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127-768x510.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FThe-MOHAN-Foundation-team_11zon-1717421127-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351954%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22997%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20team.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESignificant%20rise%20in%20numbers%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Global%20Observatory%20on%20Donation%20and%20Transplantation%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20deceased%20organ%20donations%20post%20COVID-19.%20It%20surpassed%20a%20milestone%20by%20transitioning%20from%20three-digit%20donations%20to%20four%20digits%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20having%20had%20a%20total%20of%201%2C037%20deceased%20donors%20in%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20India%20conducted%20a%20total%20of%2012%2C526%20kidney%20transplants%2C%2010%2C896%20from%20living%20donors%20and%201%2C630%20from%20deceased%20donors.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20were%204%2C173%20liver%20transplants%2C%20including%203%2C338%20from%20living%20donors%20and%20828%20from%20deceased%20donors.%20There%20were%20221%20total%20heart%20transplants%2C%20191%20liver%2C%2021%20pancreas%20and%2014%20small%20bowel%20transplants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%20faced%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20%26amp%3B%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20some%20of%20the%20challenges%20in%20deceased%20organ%20donation%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHuge%20demand-supply%20gap.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPoor%20infrastructure%2C%20especially%20in%20government%20hospitals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELack%20of%20awareness%20of%20brain%20death%20among%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPoor%20rate%20of%20brain%20death%20certification%20by%20hospitals.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELack%20of%20awareness%20and%20negative%20attitude%20towards%20deceased%20organ%20donation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELack%20of%20organised%20systems%20for%20organ%20procurement%20from%20deceased%20donors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaintenance%20of%20standards%20in%20organ%20retrieval%2C%20tissue%20banking%2C%20and%20transplantation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHigh%20cost%20of%20transplantation%2C%20especially%20for%20uninsured%20and%20poor%20patients.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20DGHS%2C%20the%20National%20Organ%20and%20Tissue%20Transplant%20Organisation%20(NOTTO)%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20following%20actions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaintaining%20the%20waiting%20list%20of%20terminally%20ill%20patients%20requiring%20transplants%20%E2%80%93%20with%20details%20of%20hospital%2C%20organ%20needed%2C%20blood%20group%20and%20age%20of%20patient%2C%20urgency%2C%20and%20seniority%20in%20the%20waiting%20list.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMatching%20recipients%20with%20donors.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENetworking%20with%20transplant%20centres%2C%20retrieval%20centres%20and%20tissue%20banks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECoordination%20of%20all%20activities%20required%20for%20procurement%20of%20organs%20and%20tissues%2C%20including%20medico-legal%20aspects.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAssigning%20the%20organ%20retrieval%20team%20and%20making%20arrangements%20for%20transporting%20the%20organs%20to%20the%20allocated%20locations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20796px)%20100vw%2C%20796px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22796%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Actress%20Revathi%20holding%20up%20her%20donor%20card.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930.jpg%20796w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FActress-Revathi-holding-up-a-donor-card-1717420930-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351951%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EActress%20Revathi%20holding%20up%20her%20donor%20card.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECounselling%20the%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Dr%20Shroff%20set%20up%20a%20protocol%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Ramachandra%20Protocol%E2%80%99%20while%20asking%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20consent%20for%20organ%20donation.%20The%20doctors%20would%20start%20by%20asking%20for%20eye%20donation%20first%20since%20it%20was%20already%20popular%2C%20and%20then%20for%20the%20other%20organs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTalking%20about%20organ%20donation%20is%20not%20easy%20at%20a%20time%20of%20grief.%20We%20need%20to%20treat%20the%20grieving%20family%20sensitively%20and%20support%20them.%20We%20have%20to%20first%20convey%20to%20the%20family%20that%20their%20loved%20one%20is%20brain%20dead.%20We%20need%20to%20then%20explain%20what%20brain%20death%20is.%20We%20let%20the%20message%20sink%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20to%20six%20hours%2C%20before%20we%20switch%20off%20the%20ventilator%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20family%20whether%20they%20wish%20to%20donate%20the%20organs.%20We%20tell%20them%20that%20they%20can%20save%20many%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20brain%20deaths%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F131027%2Fblood-donation-record-rotary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edue%20to%20road%20accidents%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Doctors%20have%20two%20to%20three%20days%20after%20brain%20deaths%20to%20do%20a%20transplant%20surgery.%20Certifying%20a%20brain%20death%20is%20a%20complex%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20the%20counsellors%20start%20a%20conversation%20with%20the%20family.%20If%20the%20family%20is%20convinced%2C%20multiple%20organs%20are%20harvested%20and%20distributed%20for%20transplant%20as%20per%20the%20waiting%20list%20of%20recipients.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20team%20work%20involved%20which%20is%20done%20by%20coordinators%20trained%20by%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAge%20is%20no%20bar%20for%20organ%20donation.%20Our%20oldest%20donor%20was%20an%2088-year-old%20trustee%20of%20the%20Gangaram%20Hospital.%20When%20he%20was%20declared%20brain%20dead%2C%20his%20kidneys%20and%20liver%20were%20transplanted.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20cautious%20about%20taking%20the%20heart%20and%20lungs%20of%20a%20donor%20who%20is%20above%2060%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Shroff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201768px)%20100vw%2C%201768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWith-a-donor-family-in-Seattle-US_11zon-1717420865.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20a%20function%20to%20felicitate%20organ%20donor%20families%20in%20Seattle.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWith-a-donor-family-in-Seattle-US_11zon-1717420865.jpg%201768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWith-a-donor-family-in-Seattle-US_11zon-1717420865-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWith-a-donor-family-in-Seattle-US_11zon-1717420865-500x327.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FWith-a-donor-family-in-Seattle-US_11zon-1717420865-768x502.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2