enor%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Tribute%20to%20Life%20for%20Commonwealth%20Organ%20Donation%20Project%E2%80%99.%20He%20is%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20establishing%20the%20%E2%80%98Indian%20Organ%20Transplant%20Registry%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Indian%20Society%20of%20Organ%20Transplantation.%20This%20registry%2C%20a%20first%20in%20Asia%2C%20has%20been%20crucial%20for%20compiling%20data%20on%20kidney%20transplants%20in%20India%20and%20analysing%20their%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shroff%20believes%20that%20Indians%20are%20very%20emotional%20people%3B%20very%20giving%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20just%20some%20distrust%20with%20the%20healthcare%20system%20that%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20care%20of.%20More%20people%20will%20definitely%20come%20forward%20to%20donate%20the%20organs%20of%20loved%20ones%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20conviction.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20surgeon%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20humbled%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20programme.%20During%20organ%20donations%2C%20I%20witness%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%93%20the%20profound%20grief%20of%20losing%20a%20loved%20one%20and%20the%20overwhelming%20joy%20and%20hope%20when%20a%20family%20member%20receives%20an%20organ.%20It%20truly%20embodies%20the%20cycle%20of%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717422349000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FLaunch-of-MOHAN-Foundation-in-1997-in-Chennai-1717420294.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20Sunil%20Shroff%2C%20a%20renal%20transplant%20surgeon%2C%20established%20the%20MOHAN%20Foundation%20in%201997%20after%20facing%20criticism%20abroad%20over%20the%20rising%20kidney%20transplant%20scams%20in%20India.%20His%20organisation%20educates%20and%20empowers%20people%20to%20take%2