0the%20horror%20of%20staining%20continues%20for%20most%20of%20our%20lives.%20This%20is%20a%20familiar%20story%20to%20any%20woman%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20same%20for%20Ira%20Guha%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Asan%2C%20a%20menstrual%20cup%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20used%20to%20be%20quite%20athletic%20as%20a%20kid%20and%20run%20around.%20I%20loved%20being%20outdoors%20and%20was%20an%20active%20basketball%20player%20in%20my%20school.%20I%20remember%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337583%2Ftulsi-village-chhattisgarh-youtube-village-hummer-studios-being-chhattisgarhiya-alwa-jalwa-gold-cg04%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20in%20Chhattisgarh%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20state-level%20game%20and%20being%20on%20my%20period.%20There%20were%20no%20bins%20in%20the%20school%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20carry%20the%20soiled%20pad%20in%20my%20bag%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20feeling%20disgusted%20and%20embarrassed%20all%20day%20are%20some%20of%20her%20core%20experiences%20that%20shaped%20her%20as%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20menstrual%20hygiene%20business%2C%20she%20says.%20With%20her%20company%20Asan%2C%20she%20has%20helped%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%2060%20villages%20in%20Karnataka%20switch%20to%20menstrual%20cups%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cup%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20periods%20comfortable%20for%20every%20woman.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20rural%20women%2C%20menstrual%20cups%20can%20help%20make%20periods%20easier%20and%20healthier%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20of%20Asan%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20when%20she%20was%2018%20to%20pursue%20her%20higher%20education.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20as%20a%20management%20consultant%20in%20London%20and%20kept%20visiting%20home%20every%20once%20in%20a%20while.%20In%202016-17%2C%20the%20movie%20Padman%20was%20getting%20very%20popular%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20conversation%20around%20menstrual%20hygiene%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20one%20of%20her%20visits%20during%20this%20time%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20that%20our%20cook%20was%20on%20leave%20and%20I%20had%20called%20to%20ask%20the%20reason.%20She%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20a%20rash%20due%20to%20using%20cheap%20sanitary%20pads.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurious%2C%20Ira%20asked%20her%20to%20bring%20the%20pad%20once%20she%20recovered%20to%20check%20its%20quality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20could%20never%20imagine%20using%20that%20pad%2C%20as%20it%20was%20very%20harsh%20and%20the%20material%20did%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20absorbent.%20It%20was%20at%20that%20time%20that%20I%20introduced%20her%20to%20menstrual%20cups.%20I%20was%20using%20one%20in%20the%20UK%20but%20there%20were%20no%20brands%20at%20the%20time%20selling%20them%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20has%20distributed%20Asan%20cups%20to%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%20rural%20Karnataka.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-1-1717078112-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351631%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20has%20distributed%20Asan%20cups%20to%20over%2015%2C000%20women%20in%20rural%20Karnataka.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maid%20had%20questions%20and%20Ira%20patiently%20answered%20all%20of%20them.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20wanted%20to%20try%20one%20as%20I%20was%20carrying%20a%20spare%2C%20she%20instantly%20agreed.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20her%20next%20period%2C%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20she%20noticed%20any%20difference%20and%20she%20had%20some%20good%20reviews%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20maid%20was%20able%20to%20do%20her%20work%20better%20and%20in%20her%20words%20%E2%80%9Cdidn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20like%20she%20was%20on%20her%20period%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20struck%20Ira%20and%20she%20continued%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208745%2Fkerala-muhamma-village-women-sanitary-pads-harmful-menstrual-cup-use-environment-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarry%20menstrual%20cups%20for%20women%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%2C%20I%20was%20carrying%2010-15%20menstrual%20cups%20on%20one%20trip%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20quite%20organic%2C%20I%20was%20distributing%20them%20among%20gardeners%20in%20the%20society%2C%20more%20domestic%20workers%20who%20heard%20about%20it%20etc.%20Fast%20forward%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20went%20to%20study%20at%20Harvard.%20I%20was%20telling%20about%20my%20work%20in%20India%20to%20a%20professor%20who%20suggested%20that%20I%20should%20design%20my%20own%20cup%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20developed%20the%20Asan%20cup%20by%20working%20with%20an%20engineer%20at%20the%20Harvard%20Innovation%20Lab.%20We%20thoroughly%20studied%20existing%20menstrual%20cups%20in%20great%20detail%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20highest%20quality%20cups%20available%20globally.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20Asan%20different%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20research%20process%20and%20the%20hurdles%20she%20faced%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20product%20development%2C%20I%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20getting%20qualitative%20feedback%20on%20the%20usage%20of%20my%20cups%2C%20as%20I%20had%20distributed%20many%20cups%20throughout%20India.%20I%20needed%20detailed%20feedback%20about%20issues%20like%20leaking%2C%20overflowing%2C%20and%20comfort%2C%20but%20people%20weren%E2%80%99t%20sharing%20these%20openly%20with%20me.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%2C%20Ira%20included%20every%20single%20one%20of%20her%20friends%20in%20the%20user%20group.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20women%20across%20the%20US%20and%20UK%2C%20primarily%20contacts%20of%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20were%20willing%20to%20provide%20detailed%20feedback%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20challenge%20was%20the%20scepticism%20around%20people%20using%20menstrual%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20told%20me%20that%20India%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20such%20a%20product%20and%20that%20women%20should%20stick%20to%20traditional%20methods.%20I%20overcame%20this%20challenge%20because%20I%20am%20a%20user%20of%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20myself%2C%20and%20it%20has%20transformed%20my%20life.%20I%20can%20sleep%20through%20the%20night%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261342%2Farpita-double-amputee-yoga-fitness-instructor-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20swim%2C%20do%20yoga%2C%20and%20run%20half%20a%20%3C%2Fa%3Emarathon%20comfortably.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20experience%2C%20along%20with%20the%20positive%20feedback%20from%20my%20early%20user%20group%E2%80%94including%20domestic%20workers%20and%20other%20women%20who%20adapted%20to%20the%20cup%20instantly%E2%80%94showed%20me%20that%20not%20only%20are%20women%20ready%20for%20this%2C%20but%20they%20are%20also%20calling%20out%20for%20it%20because%20the%20current%20products%20are%20of%20poor%20quality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Ira%E2%80%99s%20personal%20experience%20and%20the%20experiences%20of%20women%20around%20her%20that%20gave%20her%20the%20conviction%20to%20challenge%20those%20who%20said%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20and%20insertable%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20woman%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20need%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20asserts.%20Ira%20came%20out%20with%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20in%20the%20year%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cups%20come%20with%20a%20cloth%20bag%20and%20an%20instruction%20manual%20in%20the%20local%20language.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-2-1717078454-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-351638%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20cups%20come%20with%20a%20cloth%20bag%20and%20an%20instruction%20manual%20in%20the%20local%20language.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20utility-based%20product%2C%20Ira%20enlists%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20an%20Asan%20Cup.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20costs%20just%20as%20much%20as%20six%20months%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20pads%20but%20can%20be%20reused%20for%20ten%20years.%20Secondly%2C%20sustainability%3A%20One%20Asan%20Cup%E2%80%99s%20life%20is%20equal%20to%20using%202%2C500%20pads%20or%20tampons.%20Thirdly%2C%20effectiveness%3A%20One%20Asan%20Cup%20holds%20up%20to%20three%20times%20more%20than%20your%20average%20pad%2C%20so%20you%20can%20go%20up%20to%2012%20hours%20without%20changing%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNumber%20four%20is%20safety.%20Unlike%20pads%20and%20tampons%20which%20may%20contain%20undisclosed%20ingredients%2C%20the%20Asan%20cup%20is%20made%20of%20medical-grade%20silicone%2C%20certified%20safe%20for%20health.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20finally%20discretion%20and%20convenience.%20The%20compact%20size%20of%20the%20Asan%20cup%20ensures%20discreet%20use%2C%20allowing%20users%20to%20maintain%20privacy%20about%20their%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20avoiding%20the%20potential%20stigma%20associated%20with%20visible%20pads%20or%20cloth%20rags%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20mention%20the%20reduction%20of%20sanitary%20pad%20waste%20which%20is%20reversed%20by%20the%20use%20of%20a%20menstrual%20cup%2C%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20reach%20rural%20women%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20women%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Asan%20also%20has%20a%20comprehensive%20behavioural%20change%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20programme%20to%20onboard%20and%20educate%20people%20on%20using%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%20The%20key%20to%20our%20behavioural%20change%20model%20is%20that%20education%20must%20come%20from%20a%20trusted%20source.%20For%20example%2C%20as%20someone%20from%20Bengaluru%20whose%20first%20language%20is%20English%2C%20I%20might%20not%20be%20a%20trusted%20source%20in%20a%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20we%20hired%20local%20social%20workers%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20use%20the%20cups%20themselves.%20They%20then%20trained%20rural%20women%20on%20how%20to%20use%20the%20cup%2C%20which%20eliminated%20scepticism%20because%20the%20information%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20trusted%20source.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20every%20Asan%20Cup%20the%20company%20sells%2C%20they%20donate%20one%20for%20free%2C%20primarily%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317722%2Fmumbai-entrepreneurs-start-marketplace-for-ngo-products-jhappi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20through%20their%20NGO%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20collaborate%20with%20various%20NGO%20partners%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20factories%20to%20offer%20subsidised%20schemes%2C%20making%20the%20Asan%20Cup%20more%20accessible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIra%20engages%20with%20women%20from%20SHG%2C%20trains%20them%20and%20then%20sends%20them%20to%20villages%20to%20introduce%20women%20with%20the%20Asan%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ira%20Guha%2C%20founder%20of%20Asan%20Cup.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fasan-cup-3-1717078377.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuplo