%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E.%20They%20taught%20me%20the%20procedure%20as%20well%20but%20I%20had%20never%20imagined%20this%20would%20become%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20to%20me%20later%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2036-year-old%2C%20who%20now%20earns%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelling%20the%20flavoured%20salt%20has%20changed%20not%20only%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20rural%20women%20but%20also%20Sandeep%2C%20who%20was%20once%20thrown%20out%20of%20his%20home%20for%20bringing%20disgrace%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20in%20the%20Army.%20When%20I%20told%20my%20family%20that%20I%20intended%20to%20sell%20salt%2C%20they%20were%20disappointed%20in%20me.%20My%20relatives%20mocked%20us%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20do%20better%20jobs.%20For%20Army%20persons%2C%20dignity%20is%20very%20prestigious%20and%20no%20one%20found%20dignity%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257903%2Futtarakhand-startup-himshakti-pahadi-namak-pink-salt-harshit-sahdev-ancient-food-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eselling%20salts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20family%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20heading%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction%20and%20that%20I%20was%20possessed%20by%20some%20hill%20ghost!%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20believed%20me%20only%20after%20six%20months%20when%20my%20work%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20news.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20who%20are%20in%20the%20US%2C%20are%20buying%20luxurious%20cars.%20Often%2C%20they%20asked%20me%20to%20join%20them%20and%20earn%20handsome%20salaries.%20But%20here%2C%20when%20I%20see%20happy%20families%20getting%20financial%20independence%20through%20our%20work%2C%20it%20motivates%20me%20to%20work%20further.%20No%20other%20achievement%20could%20give%20us%20the%20contentment%20we%20experience%20through%20this%20work.%20Every%20night%2C%20I%20sleep%20well%20knowing%2080%